<h4>Map Grid</h4>
<p>A pure ember implementation of an over-head 2d grid.</p>
<p>It's neither a material nor a bootstrap asset</p>
<p>Ships with scrollability, tile numeration, and possibly zooming in the future</p>


<button {{action "toggleMode"}}>
  {{#if isBuildMode}}
    Exit Build Mode
  {{else}}
    Enter Build Mode
  {{/if}}
</button>

{{#map-grid mode=mode action="build"}}
  {{#map-grid-polygon model=house}}
    {{map-grid-edge-attachment model=door}}
  {{/map-grid-polygon}}
  {{map-grid-polyline model=road}}
  {{map-grid-tile model=tile}}
{{/map-grid}}